Condition : 13 - No unit shall be occupied until a Car Park Management Plan has been submitted to and approved in writing by the Local Planning Authority. The Plan shall include the following:
o	Details and location of 20% electric vehicle charging points (min. 7kW/h) and details of a further 20% passive provision;
o	A strategy detailing how the uptake in electric vehicle charging points is monitored to bring into use passive charging points when required;
o	Details of parking layout and allocations (including details as to how the occupancy will be maximised through the lease of spaces)
o	Details of how parking outside of designated bays will be managed. 
The car parking areas shall thereafter be managed in compliance with the approved Car Park Management Plan.
